title: South
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, Mexican, Latin American, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. In a town with limited veg food this place provides some. The food is made from scratch, and tortillas are preservative-free. Menu vegetarian items are clearly labeled; some can be made vegan by request no cheese and no crema. Has a complimentary salsa bar. Creative cocktails. Live Music Fridays from 8pm-10pm. Happy hour weekdays 4:30pm-5:30pm.
